<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="legend-page legend-hell">
  <div class="container legend-shell">
    <div class="legend-grid">
      <div class="legend-poster-wrap hell-glow">
        <div class="legend-poster">
          <div class="legend-coming-soon">Coming Soon</div>
          <div class="legend-placeholder">
            <div class="legend-placeholder-box">
              <div class="legend-placeholder-text">Beelzebub Image Placeholder</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="legend-copy">
        <div class="legend-badges">
          <span class="legend-badge hell">Hell</span>
          <span class="legend-tier">Cataclysmic</span>
        </div>

        <h1>Beelzebub</h1>
        <p class="legend-role">Prince of Corruption</p>
        <p class="legend-lead">
          Beelzebub is rot, seduction, and spiritual contamination crowned with authority.
        </p>

        <div class="legend-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/">Return Home</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/characters/apollyon">View Apollyon</a>
        </div>

        <div class="legend-panels">
          <div class="legend-panel">
            <h2>Description</h2>
            <p>
              Beelzebub does not always destroy by force first. He infects, corrupts, and
              weakens from within. He is the kind of terror that turns conviction into compromise
              and strength into collapse. Wherever he moves, purity is tested and loyalty begins to rot.
            </p>

            <div class="legend-power-grid">
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Corruption Aura</h3><p>Spreads decay through minds, systems, and souls.</p></div>
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Temptation Rule</h3><p>Turns weakness into willing surrender.</p></div>
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Demonic Authority</h3><p>Commands oppressive darkness with calculated precision.</p></div>
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Internal Collapse</h3><p>Destroys kingdoms from the inside out.</p></div>
            </div>

            <div class="legend-quote">“Some kingdoms do not burn first. They rot.”</div>
          </div>

          <div class="legend-panel">
            <h2>Profile</h2>
            <div class="legend-profile">
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Faction</span><span class="legend-value">Hell</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Role</span><span class="legend-value">Prince of Corruption</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Power Theme</span><span class="legend-value">Decay / Temptation / Dominion</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Visual</span><span class="legend-value">Image Coming Soon</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Background</span><span class="legend-value">Placeholder Active</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>